"{\"uid\": \"theguardian.com-tv-and-radio-article-2024-jul-27-roy-and-hg-head-to-the-paris-olympics-2024-interview-show-people-medals-and-cheese-abc-radio-ntwnfb\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australia's favourite sportscasters are bringing their own slightly skewed style to the games, handing out cheese singles and campaigning for rugby league to be an Olympic sport  Answering the prayers of a world where too much sport is never enough, HG Nelson and Rampaging Roy Slaven - the doyen and dominatrix of satirical sportscasting - are heading to Paris to present their new ABC radio show: People, Medals and Cheese.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999523579401, \"rank\": 3.010596510356806e-08, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.285496828750102e-34, \"text\": \"HG Nelson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.729179497675448e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 383, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999855094758, \"rank\": 1.4490359921970776e-08, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After earning the ire of former prime minister John Howard with their late-90s variety show Club Buggery, Roy & HG (and their mascotFatso, the Fat-Arsed Wombat) hit the big time withThe Dream, their skewed take on Sydney's 2000 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.055252643503789e-19, \"text\": \"John Howard\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Buggery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Club Buggery\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Buggery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Buggery\"}, {\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.1649878130616815e-13, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They spoke to Guardian Australia, in character and under armed guard, to discuss the future of equestrian events, Gina Rinehart's swimming prowess and the prospect of a World Origin.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guardian Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999991177901, \"rank\": 8.819140889640725e-10, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gina Rinehart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So is People, Medals and Cheese a continuation of The Dream?\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG Nelson: No, I do not think so, because People, Medals and Cheese is radio only.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.285496828750102e-34, \"text\": \"HG Nelson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that gives us a licence to put the theatre of the mind front and centre.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We can paint a picture with words in a way that makes it seem much more scandalous and impossible to understand what possessed a triple gold medallist tobash the living daylights out of a horse.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is there still a place for equestrian events at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999991177901, \"rank\": 8.819140889640725e-10, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not have athletes flogging a live horse on television, can we?\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: I can hear the irony in your voice there.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Look, my take on this is how many countries can even afford, firstly, the clobber they wear - the jodhpurs, the dress jackets \\u2026  Roy Slaven: The boots \\u2026  HG: The boots; the hat.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let alone buy a horse!\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of these horses are worth upwards of $1m, never mind the horse float that they need to go in.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: I think the argument for dog races at theOlympic Gamesis far more compelling than for equestrian.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999991177901, \"rank\": 8.819140889640725e-10, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, you are not sitting on a dog, but you are training a dog to express itself at very high speeds over short distances.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's something that people can relate to.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All you need is a bit of flat track, and a dog.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: And meat.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The question on everyone's lips is: what happened to Fatso?\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghostly_Trio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.887622192788926e-15, \"text\": \"Fatso\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghostly_Trio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghostly_Trio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Will he be joining you in Paris?\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.729179497675448e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does the ABC have sufficient funding to buy him back from Kerry Stokes?\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999855094758, \"rank\": 1.4490359921970776e-08, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Stokes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kerry Stokes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Stokes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Stokes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Well, each city comes up with its own mascot, and in this instance it's the Olympic Phryge, which is a terrific thing.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They took a small hat, put some legs and feet under it and they have created a very engaging little character that says very little to a lot of people.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: When I saw it, I thought, \\\"hello, there is a cry for help if ever I have seen one\\\".\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you bust a few breakdancing moves in your youth, Rampaging Roy?\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Oh look, I do love breakdancing.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something I share with others; it's something I do quietly amongst myself, in the back yard.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once you get into it, it's a wonderful thing.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Great for fitness, great for balance.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: Balance!\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: That's what it's all about - I mean, when you put yourself on your head and spin, you come to a quick understanding of centrifugal and centripetal force, and how these forces act upon not only the head but the rest of the body.\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: But beforehand, for God's sake, just let people from the emergency department of your local hospital know you are doing it.\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Yes, yes.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or family and friends, just let them know that you are doing it, so that if there is silence for 48 hours, or maybe a couple of weeks, they can send out a search party.\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What measures are you taking to ensure your own security in Paris?\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3543, \"end\": 3548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.729179497675448e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Do not big-note yourself.\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not wear track suits, do not wear lanyards saying you are with the ABC or with Channel 9!\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3652, \"end\": 3655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999855094758, \"rank\": 1.4490359921970776e-08, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blend in!\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: I think it's common sense, Roy.\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carry a pack of Bega cheese - singles, because then it's easier to peel them off and hand them out.\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3738, \"end\": 3749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bega_Cheese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bega cheese\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bega_Cheese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bega_Cheese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gina Rinehart is a major financial benefactor of our swim team.\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3823, \"end\": 3836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gina Rinehart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should she go a step further and anchor the 4x100m?\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: Well, we will need super-quick swimmers at the start.\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not knocking Gina; she could probably bring it home in about four minutes.\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4016, \"end\": 4020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Holby_City\", \"score\": 0.9580274296994985, \"rank\": 0.0438114494422609, \"text\": \"Gina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Holby_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Holby_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, there is something for television, that would be an absolute winner.\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: It would certainly bring in the viewers, would not it?\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: AndBrucewould call it beautifully.\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The words ofLa Marseillaisearefrankly disturbing.\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How many times can we hear the French singing \\\"let impure blood water our fields\\\" before war breaks out?\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4335, \"end\": 4341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9996932805487246, \"rank\": 0.00024587254767086055, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: Hang on a minute.\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are talking about poetry here.\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I suppose nations have gone to war over poetry before, and I suppose they will do it again.\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: All I can say to the Aussie competitors is, let us not hear the French anthem today.\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4629, \"end\": 4635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9996932805487246, \"rank\": 0.00024587254767086055, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: Exactly.\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is one way of doing that, and that is to win gold yourself.\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"200,000 male condoms, 20,000 female condoms, 10,000 dental dams.\", \"from\": 4731, \"to\": 4795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whatever happened to saving your energies for the main event?\", \"from\": 4796, \"to\": 4857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: Well, those are offered after the main event, if you are counting sport as the main event.\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 4953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of people do not; they prefer the after-hours activity as their main event, and sport's just the thing that got them there.\", \"from\": 4954, \"to\": 5083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Yes, yes.\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think sex and sport have gone hand in hand for a hell of a long time.\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have only got to look at the shards of pottery from ancient Greece.\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5228, \"end\": 5242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999939655849802, \"rank\": 5.98166168657792e-06, \"text\": \"ancient Greece\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, you get a little bit of Greco-Roman, but the act of love is celebrated in the pots just as much.\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5274, \"end\": 5285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_world\", \"score\": 0.6102629693328281, \"rank\": 0.6365452187534233, \"text\": \"Greco-Roman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_world\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brisbane is not a hillbilly city, at leastaccording to the 2032 Olympic chief Andrew Liveris.\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5426, \"end\": 5440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Liveris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Liveris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Liveris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Liveris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What new sport can we expect to debut there?\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: RUGBY LEAGUE!\", \"from\": 5488, \"to\": 5505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's screaming out to be included in Brisbane.\", \"from\": 5506, \"to\": 5552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5543, \"end\": 5551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999986830517, \"rank\": 1.264156301854524e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Yep, yep.\", \"from\": 5554, \"to\": 5568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And rugby league we can almost guarantee - well, perhaps gold, but at least silver or bronze.\", \"from\": 5569, \"to\": 5662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Could we have a World Origin?\", \"from\": 5664, \"to\": 5693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: That's what the Olympics is!\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: That's what it would be.\", \"from\": 5730, \"to\": 5758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us say we got 40 nations together to put in a rugby league team - I'd consider that a World Origin.\", \"from\": 5759, \"to\": 5862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People, Medals and Cheese airs on ABCRadioSunday to Friday at 11am on ABC Radio and 2pm on Radio National, and can be downloaded on the ABC Listen app.\", \"from\": 5864, \"to\": 6015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5934, \"end\": 5943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.999999999398824, \"rank\": 5.967165809748326e-10, \"text\": \"ABC Radio\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 5955, \"end\": 5969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_National\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Radio National\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_National\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_National\"}, {\"begin\": 6000, \"end\": 6014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_ABC_Radio_(Australia)\", \"score\": 0.9999999998676685, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Listen app\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_ABC_Radio_(Australia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_ABC_Radio_(Australia)\"}]}]}"